Source: scurl
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Patrick Schleizer <adrelanos@riseup.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), faketime, genmkfile, ruby-ronn (>= 0.7.3)
Homepage: https://github.com/Whonix/scurl
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/Whonix/scurl
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/Whonix/scurl.git
Standards-Version: 3.9.4

Package: scurl
Architecture: all
Depends: curl, ${misc:Depends}
Description: SSL curl wrapper
 Simple wrapper called scurl, that adds "--tlsv1 --proto =https" in front of
 all invocations of "curl" when running "scurl".
 .
 For better security/usability.
 .
 Safe to remove if you are not using this.
